item.description:
"This event has been made possible through a grant submitted to the Tyngsborough Cultural Council

made possible by the Mass. Cultural Council." 

"The Tyngsboro Cultural Council is a local agency funded by the Massachusetts Cultural Council, a

state agency".  www.massculturalcouncil.org

Tickets are $10 at the door.  There is a full bar.  They are serving hamburgers or hot dogs, for an extra cost.

From the north, Exit 34 off Rt 3, then right off ramp to Westford Rd.  Sportmen's Club is on the right

at 90 Westford Rd. 

From the south, Exit 34 off Rt 3, then left off ramp to Westford Rd.   

Sportmen's Club is on the left at 90 Westford Rd.
